{"tid":2017983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國歌法算唔算香港第一條純粹國家玻璃心的惡法","createTime":"2020-05-15T11:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T11:37:10.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"961e065a160331d6ce6cdc2e8c6b506bed331aa3","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:00:41.000Z","msg":"其他法律或惡法都有利有弊，或者有維穩目的。<br />\n<br />\n國歌法純粹玻璃心，捐人權但又冇利益或維穩目的，國歌唔比人鬧得係純玻璃心，鬧國歌要判三年監。"},{"pid":"cdd6d0fe7fde1b7b9b418caddd3a286a4919be88","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"香港第一條純綷玻璃心，但又破壞人權和言論自由的法律"},{"pid":"189fd24662007a33da263db07b07533e1f869277","tid":2017983,"uid":29858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"其實杯葛匪歌 唔唱匪歌算唔算犯法？"},{"pid":"dc9b669203bc5c943737081b5016a586d75eff9b","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"國安法目的，都話要黎反港獨，反西藏獨立<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例就要黎送逃犯，不過大家覺得中共信唔過所以反對。<br />\n<br />\n國歌法目的為咩？"},{"pid":"6973c49796062f8f04b161ec51e78ae7b86da781","tid":2017983,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過左班狗一定日播夜播，要拉你話咁易，而且條蝈歌惡法有無限追溯力<br />\n<br />\n劇本黎，支共明顯想玩鎖國，要拉埋香港落水咁解姐<br />\n<br />\n支共想攬炒，我地唯有奉陪，誠懇呼籲外資盡快撤出香港，以保安全<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，唯有開戰<br />\n<br />\n向愛爾蘭共和軍學習<br />\n<br />\n向愛爾蘭獨立學習<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，任何行動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不受傷不被捕</strong></span>真係最重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92fa34cb2206d8f08df1979ce2e71552b563bad","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"國歌法，係全港最玻璃心，最無聊，最無謂的法律。<br />\n但又破壞言論自由和人權。"},{"pid":"e62a6a96328ab848abb77a3ab68c526c74a99e22","tid":2017983,"uid":61831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"國旗法？"},{"pid":"63236807db7b39f036fb4b30770b65259c4f0e07","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"咁鬼小氣，被人噓都唔得，仲話自己係大國。<br />\n小國咋嘩。"},{"pid":"98575d55d8e69afd7d7be9ced022e86f3e98395b","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e62a6a96328ab848abb77a3ab68c526c74a99e22","tid":2017983,"uid":61831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"國旗法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"國旗法要用行動做出黎先犯，<br />\n國歌法連用口表達都唔得"},{"pid":"c92eee611a8a8a579a4d05b6dfc3b5b84613214f","tid":2017983,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"仲要任佢演譯何謂不尊重"},{"pid":"0ef8c0c1e83dd9003f87be3b8df9c109d0b7f948","tid":2017983,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c92eee611a8a8a579a4d05b6dfc3b5b84613214f","tid":2017983,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"仲要任佢演譯何謂不尊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"用到刑事法例黎逼你尊重國歌，都幾悲衰。<br />\n<br />\n真小國。"},{"pid":"14af135ed4e453508761fbbf5c89df1885f76eda","tid":2017983,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:23:34.000Z","msg":"生咗仔女嗰啲，唔該教埋你哋個仔女認識中國國歌作者係比人批鬥死<img src=\"/assets/